Package: FloodSync
Title: Flood Mapping and Monitoring Tool
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Mark", "Lelaono", "marklelaono@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for flood mapping using a Python backend with Google Earth Engine.
    The package provides functions to create flood maps using Google Earth Engine.
    It allows users to visualize and analyze flood data in R.
    The package is designed to be user-friendly and efficient, making it easy for
    researchers and practitioners to work with flood data.
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0.0),
    reticulate,
    sf,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    leaflet,
    httr,
    jsonlite
